--- Task 2 Demo: JSON Schema Classification & Extraction ---

Sample chat #1: Hey, I'm Priya Sharma, 27 years old from Bengaluru. You can reach me at priya.sharma@example.com or +91 98765 43210.
Raw extracted: {
  "name": "Priya Sharma",
  "email": "priya.sharma@example.com",
  "phone": "98765 4321",
  "location": "Bengaluru",
  "age": 27
}
Validation result: {
  "valid": true,
  "errors": [],
  "cleaned": {
    "name": "Priya Sharma",
    "email": "priya.sharma@example.com",
    "phone": "98765 4321",
    "location": "Bengaluru",
    "age": 27
  }
}

Sample chat #2: Hello, my name is John Doe. Email: john.doe@acme.co. I'm 34 and live in Austin.
Raw extracted: {
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@acme.co",
  "location": "Austin",
  "age": 34
}
Validation result: {
  "valid": true,
  "errors": [],
  "cleaned": {
    "name": "John Doe",
    "email": "john.doe@acme.co",
    "location": "Austin",
    "age": 34
  }
}

Sample chat #3: Hi, it's Maria. Call me at (555) 123-4567. I live in New York.
Raw extracted: {
  "phone": "(555) 123-4567",
  "location": "New York"
}
Validation result: {
  "valid": true,
  "errors": [],
  "cleaned": {
    "phone": "(555) 123-4567",
    "location": "New York"
  }
}

--- End of demo script.
Notes:
- To run model-powered summarization/extraction, set GROQ_API_KEY environment variable or replace placeholder in the script.
- This file is ready to be uploaded to Google Colab as a single cell (or split into cells for readability).
- Commit this file to your GitHub repo for submission. Include a README describing usage and where to set API keys.
